headline: Edgecore Networks Sets New Benchmark for AI Infrastructure with World’s First 102.4T Open Networking Switches
summary: HSINCHU, Taiwan, February 23, 2026--Edgecore Networks, a leading provider of open networking technology and solutions, today announced the launch of its next-generation 102.4T data center switches: the AIS1600-64O and AIS800-128O. Powered by Broadcom’s latest 3nm Tomahawk® 6 chips, these platforms are engineered to meet the massive bandwidth and low-latency demands of hyperscale AI/ML clusters and next-generation advanced cloud fabrics.
